description:
Star Wars the Acolyte is a true example of what happens when you give a gaggle of inexperienced writers a LOT of money. It's quite clear that the show is not only bad, but that the writers have no idea how to use even the basic tools of writing.

#starwars #theacolyte #disneystarwars
title: Star Wars The Acolyte is Garbage part 7 #theacolyte #starwars
